911. What is your emergency?

904
01:33:19,600 --> 01:33:22,019
Yes, hello?

905
01:33:22,060 --> 01:33:24,146
( screaming )

906
01:33:29,818 --> 01:33:32,112
( Allison continues screaming )

907
01:34:27,960 --> 01:34:29,920
( whimpering )

908
01:34:38,762 --> 01:34:41,890
( stairs creaking )

909
01:34:41,932 --> 01:34:44,059
Wendy: Allison?

910
01:34:44,101 --> 01:34:47,062
