913
01:35:13,881 --> 01:35:15,924
( coughing )

914
01:35:39,072 --> 01:35:40,449
( heart beating )

915
01:35:40,491 --> 01:35:42,493
Boy!

916
01:35:47,956 --> 01:35:50,167
( groaning )

917
