( footsteps )

918
01:36:07,684 --> 01:36:10,229
- ( thunder rumbling )
- ( chimes tinkling )

919
01:36:31,083 --> 01:36:33,418
l understand now

920
01:36:33,460 --> 01:36:35,587
why they run...

921
01:36:38,715 --> 01:36:40,926
that even a dumb animal

922
01:36:43,846 --> 01:36:46,473
knows when it's been betrayed.

923
01:36:57,860 --> 01:37:00,320
Do you feel betrayed?

924
01:37:03,407 --> 01:37:05,200
No.

925
01:37:05,242 --> 01:37:07,744
That's why you didn't run.

926
01:37:07,786 --> 01:37:10,998
'Cause you knew
you had it coming.

927
01:37:14,460 --> 01:37:17,963
( footsteps )

928
01:37:19,590 --> 01:37:23,218
You--

929
01:37:23,260 --> 01:37:25,762
you never ran.

930
01:37:31,477 --> 01:37:33,353
My boy.

931
01:37:45,616 --> 01:37:47,910
Thank you.

932
01:37:47,951 --> 01:37:50,245
( screaming )

